- ✅ Filter logic preserved (returnflag = 'R')
- ✅ Join order and cardinalities unchanged

### Code Quality
- Clean mmap-based loading avoids allocation overhead
- Eliminated duplicate vector allocations from filtering step
- Used struct casting for safe binary format parsing

